                            style="color:gold; text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">A new video</a> about
                        GDMC was recently published on Youtube by the AI and Games channel. Check it out!<br><br>As some
                        may have noticed, <a href="http://gendesignmc.wikidot.com/"
                            style="color:gold; text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">we now have our own
                            wiki!</a> It is being actively updated by both organizers and members of the community, so
